Frequently Asked Questions

My table didn't extract correctly. What should I do?
Open the Advanced Controls in the sidebar, disable "Adaptive Row Tolerance", and manually adjust the slider until the grid aligns with your data.

Is my data sent to a server?
No. All Vision processing happens securely and locally on your Apple device.

How do I export my data?
Once you have extracted your rows, click the "Export Data to CSV" button in the sidebar to save the file locally to your machine.


